::Bazooka::
    
    Inside the lab he could feel the changes. This isn't right. He thought to 
himself, he shouldn't have fins or a mouth filled with sharp teeth. Soon 
everything went dark.

    When he awoke he knew who he was, but he was not Bazooka. He knew that 
something happened and that he should be something else. But he knew that he 
liked the body he was in. And he remembered two different pasts. Almost like 
he had a new Spark. His name is CyberShark. The water began to drain from his 
birth place, he knew he must transform.
    "CyberShark, Transform." He declared. He was now in an impressive robot 
mode. (Putting a pic in the next mail) He walked out to greet all the people, 
but he still remembered most of them. Bobertron, Magmatron, Shredder, 
Mantella, and one named Bazooka. But if he remembered he killed Bazooka, or 
was that an actual memory?
